{"tid":1393315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「⾹港⺠意研所」開拓新的研究方法 市民可自願參與調查","createTime":"2019-08-01T05:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T14:05:36.000Z","uid":268009,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd0cf8835b75cfcc3d5c12ce27bbbdca49ba724","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:02:03.000Z","msg":"LINK: <a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/hkpop-panel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fhkpop-panel&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl597g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=36240980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/hkpop-panel</a> <br />\n<br />\n⾹港⺠意研究所正在開展⼀系列多⽤途⽽獨⽴運作的<span style=\"color: red;\">「⾹港⺠研意⾒群組」，分為概率及⾮概率組群，每樣兩組，分別名為⾹港市⺠代表組群、⾹港市⺠⾃結組群、⾹港⻘年代表組群、⾹港⻘年⾃結組群。研究所同時歡迎個別⼈⼠和團體，以同樣設計合作開辦更多組群，包括網⺠組群、銀髮組群、少數族組群等等。</span><br />\n<br />\n顧名思義，<span style=\"color: red;\">概率組群只包括以隨機抽樣⽅式組成，能夠代表⾹港特定⼈⼝的⼈⼠。</span>有關⼈⼠須由研究所隨機發出邀請，並在同意相關條款後加⼊組群，⽅能成為組群成員，⾃薦參與者概不受理。<span style=\"color: red;\">概率組群的成員主要來⾃電話抽樣，其意⾒應可準確代表⾹港⼈⼝當中</span>，相關組別⼈⼠對某些特定題⽬的主流意⾒。<br />\n<br />\n研究所現時設⽴兩個⾮概率組群，⽇後會漸次增加。這些<span style=\"color: red;\">⾮概率組群屬於開放組織，歡迎任何⾃認符合資格的市⺠參加。</span>⾮概率組群將會迅速發展，為⽬標⼈⼝提供有效和快速的渠道，抒發思想和意⾒。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有意加⼊意⾒群組的市⺠，需要先填寫申請表格，提供正確無誤的背景資料。群組成員會定期獲邀參加不同題⽬的調查，包括電話調查、當⾯訪問或以⽂字查訪。</span>每個調查會列明研究項⽬、⽅法、獎勵和⼤概結束⽇⼦，成員可以選擇拒絕參加，但積極接受邀請的成員則有更⼤機會獲得⾦錢或物品獎勵。⾹港⺠研意⾒群組是具有代表性的⺠意組織，從中收集的意⾒對於⾹港⺠研的⼯作極爲重要。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">⾹港⺠意研究所珍惜不同政治、經濟、社會背景⼈⼠的意⾒，歡迎所有⾹港居⺠加⼊意⾒群組，就不同議題發表意⾒。所有成員的個⼈資料不會被分享或轉賣給第三機構。研究所會確保意⾒群組不會受到錯誤或有害訊息⼲預，有秩序和健康地運作下去。</span><br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n請大家務必參與，證明民意走向有普遍認受性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b825f992f7ec08a9d8329b21ddf9ea9dd71862aa","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:04:17.000Z","msg":"希望大家知道！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n#8月5日全民罷工"},{"pid":"afc844e0cb0300de8817033d4d778eab81b87fa5","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:04:42.000Z","msg":"#8月5日全民罷工"},{"pid":"c5d4b2efb3d4e3b215f73af6f63625bdd9ca5df8","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:06:22.000Z","msg":"雖不在港，#8月5日全民罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c924c10ab3dbd6bea83055a2c123c278bace4014","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"可選擇電郵、電話、面訪進行調查！<br />\n<br />\n#8月5日全民罷工"},{"pid":"c619e4bbdb1e8ba2cc03104086e9ac3eb84fea36","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:09:02.000Z","msg":"研究的認受性好重要！！！！大家踴躍參與！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n#8月5日全民罷工"},{"pid":"704fc6f509c420146d90f66ce051a2666e9b1890","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:09:54.000Z","msg":"推埋俾屋企人一齊參與！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#8月5日全民罷工"},{"pid":"d10825b994acf92cbdbb8188e54264e18cb25a5c","tid":1393315,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:10:27.000Z","msg":"唔係好明但幫推"},{"pid":"96a3a7ff644b9a8bb2ea09e942884d864132f856","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:11:01.000Z","msg":"資訊很重要，好人一生平安！<br />\n<br />\n#8月5日全民罷工"},{"pid":"77c8a185ec0fc810b3872166c6230abbd63ddc71","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d10825b994acf92cbdbb8188e54264e18cb25a5c","tid":1393315,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:10:27.000Z","msg":"唔係好明但幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"以前既民調只限電話隨機抽出，再進行訪問。而依家既研究，除咗原有隨機抽出市民受訪外（文內所講既「概率組群」），仲新增咗「非概率組群」，屬於開放組織，只要市民願意接受研究，就可進登記接受訪問。大概就係咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#8月5日全民罷工"},{"pid":"1cefdaa0d57b251c48082c88e0637e6a6af61cbc","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:17:17.000Z","msg":"#8月5日全民罷工"},{"pid":"a0d5847fa023517b2f9a9ee606aa33640031da80","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:17:39.000Z","msg":"連登發力既時候！！！！<br />\n<br />\n#8月5日全民罷工"},{"pid":"c20b92b3e8bf9aebaae3be82b5345a7d37f78585","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:18:36.000Z","msg":"大家要知啊！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n#8月5日全民罷工"},{"pid":"7b8dc2c788957e0d4488a1cb8fce1445163a1390","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"香港加油！！！！<br />\n<br />\n#8月5日全民罷工"},{"pid":"5c9caed1244a0b3e6481aa3f1b56e6477e00e8bd","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:20:32.000Z","msg":"香港是我家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#8月5日全民罷工"},{"pid":"ab6470e713137c893230039dc9e9a616c603ae49","tid":1393315,"uid":263219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:21:06.000Z","msg":"85"},{"pid":"63bb6f0881deddaa393f213d39a03e9bc1b29f8e","tid":1393315,"uid":268009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"唔好再俾人話民意冇認受性！！！！<br />\n<br />\n#8月5日全民罷工"},{"pid":"8597128d7a36fd829214b7bbf6b60ccfc0b21056","tid":1393315,"uid":7818,"like":0,"di